additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Wheat Flour, Tomato Puree (24%), Spinach (20%), Cheese (14%) (Mozzarella Cheese (Milk, Salt, Microbial Rennet, Starter Culture), Edam Cheese (Milk, Salt, Starter Culture, Microbial Rennet, Firming Agent (Calcium Chloride))], Rapeseed Oil, Water, Yeast, Salt, Sugar, Thickener (E1412), Emulsifiers [Mono- and Diglycerides of Fatty Acids (Sourced from Vegetable Oil)], Garlic, Hydrolysed Vegetable Protein (Maize and Rapeseed), Maltodextrin, Cayenne Pepper, Caramelised Sugar, Flavouring

description: Experience the taste of an Italian Pizzeria with our thin and crispy, Italian-style pizza; deliciously topped with delicious spinach leaves, creamy garlic, Edam & mozzarella cheese and a fruity tomato sauce on a perfect thin & crispy crust.
name: Frozen Ristorante Spinaci (Spinach) Pizza
